snippet.title: BattleRise: Kingdom of Champions Trailer #1
snippet.description:
The realm of Eos faces destruction from Tiamat, a powerful force intent on imposing balance between light and dark. Backed by an intimidating group of accomplices, Tiamat is a risk to all living beings. You must unite with courageous, daring, and well-trained champions to protect Eos from these old enemies that could lead to annihilation!

Visit us on our social media so you don't miss the latest news!
